{"tid":1772247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家其實知唔知咩係黃色經濟圈？","createTime":"2019-12-06T12:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T04:27:20.000Z","uid":258112,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4f628f424237d869ec85254cac94eb7eced41ca9","tid":1772247,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">經濟圈</span></span>（大都會區、都會區集合、大經濟區）指一定區域範圍內的經濟組織實體。<br />\n<br />\n經濟圈的特點表現為內部具有比較明顯的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同質性與群體性</span></span>，與外部有着比較明確的組織和地域界限。<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色經濟圈</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個重點係在於建立一個處於我地嘅經濟組織實體<br />\n<br />\n仍然要<span style=\"color: gold;\">計算成本效益，利潤同收支平衡</span><br />\n同普通嘅營商一樣 一買一賣，<br />\n只係當中大家唔係只係以賣家買家身份做交易，<br />\n而仲有一個同路人嘅身份，<br />\n以達至<span style=\"color: gold;\">互惠互利</span>關係，從而取得雙贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係義工或者非牟利先算係黃色經濟圈入面</span></span><br />\n其他會賺錢嘅就一定係人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n舉個例子<br />\n元朗水門同清玉就做到呢種效果<br />\n仍以相近嘅價錢 賣翻佢地本來嘅商品<br />\n<br />\n同時 互相宣傳 互助互利 最後就雙贏<br />\n<br />\n係呢個經濟圈<br />\n仍然存在<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淘汰機制</span></span><br />\n你覺得嗰樣野唔實用 唔好 又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪唔好買<br />\n<br />\n商家係黃色經濟圈入面唔代表可以求其做<br />\n都係要識得營商 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">作出改善</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁先會係一個健康嘅經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n重複又重複嘅<br />\n黃店<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係局限於餐廳</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n零售 服務 等等都要有<br />\n先會擴大到個黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n12月8見啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8812331288b4eafeb199584ab0a9b311492cae3","tid":1772247,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b605c28cb5945427fa325632a211852ed1d89dc6","tid":1772247,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"第一個post 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00600c01f1305c00d4cbf725772e7ec3f269658b","tid":1772247,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"eb5618e79c4876168456cae4e13af49eac54bdcd","tid":1772247,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"749e025eb9bf5652ce0eab1a2b20ce5975da7ae1","tid":1772247,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"有用資訊 push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c05f30d01cc218bbb686320477fdf88aa1b746","tid":1772247,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁 等我幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bdbaf30eb85ac17c74631e272e077e5226324f","tid":1772247,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:13:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ceeffdb4d8f7bf63abbff0af7b20921ea823c30e","tid":1772247,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T01:04:34.000Z","msg":"叫雞經濟圈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53848843f030c9c2acd80bc064def57f660b72a","tid":1772247,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T01:05:51.000Z","msg":"<